{% comment %}
  policy-page.liquid
  Used by: page.return-policy.json, page.shipping-policy.json, page.privacy-policy.json
  GMC Requirements: Must be accessible from homepage footer, must show clear policy terms
{% endcomment %}

{% style %}
.policy-page { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #1a2b45; }
.policy-page h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 8px; color: #0e2240; }
.policy-page .policy-updated { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7a8d; margin: 0 0 40px; }
.policy-page h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin: 36px 0 12px; color: #0e2240; border-bottom: 2px solid #cff394; padding-bottom: 8px; }
.policy-page h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 20px 0 8px; }
.policy-page p, .policy-page li { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #3d4a5c; }
.policy-page ul, .policy-page ol { padding-left: 24px; margin: 12px 0; }
.policy-page li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
.policy-page a { color: #0e2240; font-weight: 600; }
.policy-page a:hover { color: #3caa55; }
.policy-highlight {
  background: #f0f9f4;
  border: 1px solid #a8e060;
  border-left: 4px solid #3caa55;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 20px 0;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #1a3320;
}
.policy-highlight strong { color: #0e2240; }
.policy-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; }
.policy-table th { background: #0e2240; color: #fff; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
.policy-table td { padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
.policy-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #f8fafb; }
.policy-contact-box {
  background: #0e2240;
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 28px 32px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.policy-contact-box h3 { color: #cff394; margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 18px; }
.policy-contact-box p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 14px; }
.policy-contact-box a { color: #cff394; }
{% endstyle %}

{%- assign policy_type = page.handle -%}

<div class="policy-page">

  {%- if policy_type == 'return-policy' or policy_type == 'returns' or policy_type == 'refund-policy' -%}
  {%- comment -%} ══ RETURN & REFUND POLICY ══ {%- endcomment -%}
  <h1>Return & Refund Policy</h1>
  <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Effective: 1 January 2024</p>

  <div class="policy-highlight">
    <strong>Quick Summary:</strong> We offer a 30-day return window on physical products in original condition. Digital services and software licences are non-refundable once delivered. Contact us within 30 days of purchase to start a return.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Overview</h2>
  <p>EvoTech Digital (ABN: 72 375 743 898) is committed to your satisfaction. This Return & Refund Policy applies to all purchases made through <a href="{{ request.origin }}">evotech.au</a> and governs your rights under the Australian Consumer Law (ACL).</p>

  <h2>2. Your Rights Under Australian Consumer Law</h2>
  <p>Under the ACL, you are entitled to a remedy if a product or service:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Has a major failure or does not match its description</li>
    <li>Is not fit for the purpose you told us about</li>
    <li>Does not meet acceptable quality standards</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Nothing in this policy limits your rights under the ACL.</p>

  <h2>3. Return Eligibility — Physical Products</h2>
  <table class="policy-table">
    <tr><th>Condition</th><th>Eligible for Return?</th><th>Remedy</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Faulty/defective product</td><td>✅ Yes</td><td>Full refund or replacement</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Wrong item sent</td><td>✅ Yes</td><td>Correct item sent + return postage covered</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Damaged in transit</td><td>✅ Yes</td><td>Full refund or replacement</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Change of mind (unopened)</td><td>✅ Yes (30 days)</td><td>Refund minus 15% restocking fee</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Change of mind (opened)</td><td>❌ No</td><td>—</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Used or damaged by customer</td><td>❌ No</td><td>—</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>Return Conditions</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Items must be returned within <strong>30 days</strong> of the delivery date</li>
    <li>Items must be in original, unused condition with all original packaging, accessories and documentation</li>
    <li>Proof of purchase (order number or tax invoice) must be provided</li>
    <li>Software with activated licence keys are non-returnable once activated</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Software licences (once delivered or activated)</li>
    <li>Managed IT service plans (once service delivery has commenced)</li>
    <li>Custom-configured or special-order hardware</li>
    <li>Consumables (cables, batteries, ink) once opened</li>
    <li>Items purchased on final sale or clearance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. How to Return an Item</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a> or call <a href="tel:+61466911816">+61 466 911 816</a> within 30 days</li>
    <li>Quote your order number and reason for return</li>
    <li>We will issue a Return Merchandise Authorisation (RMA) number within 2 business days</li>
    <li>Pack the item securely with the RMA number clearly marked on the outer packaging</li>
    <li>Ship to the return address provided — we recommend using tracked postage</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>6. Refund Processing</h2>
  <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund within <strong>5 business days</strong>. Approved refunds are processed to your original payment method within <strong>5–10 business days</strong>.</p>

  <h2>7. Return Shipping Costs</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Faulty, wrong, or damaged items:</strong> EvoTech Digital covers return postage</li>
    <li><strong>Change of mind:</strong> Customer is responsible for return shipping costs</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="policy-contact-box">
    <h3>Questions About Returns?</h3>
    <p>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a></p>
    <p>📞 Phone: <a href="tel:+61466911816">+61 466 911 816</a></p>
    <p>⏰ Mon–Fri, 8:00am–6:00pm AWST</p>
  </div>

  {%- elsif policy_type == 'shipping-policy' or policy_type == 'shipping' or policy_type == 'delivery-policy' -%}
  {%- comment -%} ══ SHIPPING POLICY ══ {%- endcomment -%}
  <h1>Shipping & Delivery Policy</h1>
  <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>

  <div class="policy-highlight">
    <strong>Quick Summary:</strong> We ship Australia-wide. Most orders dispatch within 1 business day. Standard delivery 2–7 business days. Express available. Free shipping on orders over $150.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Dispatch Times</h2>
  <p>Orders placed before <strong>2:00pm AWST on business days</strong> are typically dispatched the same day. Orders placed after 2:00pm or on weekends/public holidays dispatch the next business day.</p>
  <p>During peak periods or for custom-configured hardware, dispatch may take 2–3 business days. You will be notified by email if your order is delayed.</p>

  <h2>2. Shipping Options & Estimated Delivery</h2>
  <table class="policy-table">
    <tr><th>Shipping Method</th><th>Cost</th><th>Estimated Delivery (Perth)</th><th>Estimated Delivery (Other States)</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Standard Shipping</td><td>$9.95</td><td>1–3 business days</td><td>3–7 business days</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Express Shipping</td><td>$19.95</td><td>Next business day*</td><td>1–3 business days</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Free Shipping</td><td>Free (orders $150+)</td><td>2–5 business days</td><td>3–7 business days</td></tr>
  </table>
  <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7a8d;">*Next business day delivery available to metro areas only. Remote/regional WA may vary.</p>

  <h2>3. Shipping Coverage</h2>
  <p>We ship to all states and territories of Australia. We do not currently ship internationally.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Perth Metro:</strong> Fastest dispatch and delivery, same-day delivery available on request (contact us)</li>
    <li><strong>WA Regional:</strong> Standard delivery 3–8 business days</li>
    <li><strong>Eastern States (NSW, VIC, QLD, SA):</strong> 3–6 business days standard</li>
    <li><strong>NT, TAS:</strong> 5–10 business days standard</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Tracking Your Order</h2>
  <p>All orders include a tracking number sent to your email address upon dispatch. You can also track your order at <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}">evotech.au</a> using your order number, or contact us at <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a>.</p>

  <h2>5. Delivery Issues</h2>
  <h3>Lost in Transit</h3>
  <p>If your order has not arrived within the maximum estimated delivery window, please contact us immediately. We will investigate with the carrier and arrange a replacement or refund.</p>
  <h3>Damaged in Transit</h3>
  <p>If your order arrives damaged, please photograph the damage and contact us within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong> at <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a>. We will arrange a replacement at no cost.</p>
  <h3>Incorrect Address</h3>
  <p>Please ensure your delivery address is correct at checkout. We cannot redirect packages after dispatch. If a package is returned to us due to an incorrect address, re-shipping costs will apply.</p>

  <h2>6. Digital Goods & Services</h2>
  <p>Software licences, Microsoft 365 subscriptions and other digital products are delivered electronically via email within <strong>2 hours of payment confirmation</strong> (during business hours). No physical shipment applies.</p>

  <div class="policy-contact-box">
    <h3>Shipping Questions?</h3>
    <p>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a></p>
    <p>📞 Phone: <a href="tel:+61466911816">+61 466 911 816</a></p>
    <p>⏰ Mon–Fri, 8:00am–6:00pm AWST</p>
  </div>

  {%- else -%}
  {%- comment -%} ══ PRIVACY POLICY (default) ══ {%- endcomment -%}
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>

  <div class="policy-highlight">
    <strong>Summary:</strong> EvoTech Digital collects only the data needed to provide our services. We never sell your personal information. You have the right to access, correct or delete your data at any time.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
  <p>EvoTech Digital (ABN: 72 375 743 898, "EvoTech", "we", "us", "our") operates the website <a href="{{ request.origin }}">evotech.au</a>. We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with the <strong>Privacy Act 1988 (Cth)</strong> and the <strong>Australian Privacy Principles (APPs)</strong>.</p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>Information you provide directly:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Name, email address, phone number when you contact us or create an account</li>
    <li>Billing and delivery address for purchases</li>
    <li>Payment information (processed securely — we do not store card details)</li>
    <li>Business name and ABN for business accounts</li>
    <li>Support requests and correspondence with our team</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Information collected automatically:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address, browser type, operating system</li>
    <li>Pages visited, time on site, referring URLs (via Google Analytics)</li>
    <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies (see Section 7)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Process and fulfil orders and service agreements</li>
    <li>Provide IT support and managed services</li>
    <li>Send order confirmations, invoices and service updates</li>
    <li>Respond to enquiries and provide customer support</li>
    <li>Send marketing communications (only with your consent)</li>
    <li>Improve our website and services through analytics</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Information Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent or trade your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Shopify (ecommerce platform), Stripe (payments), Australia Post (shipping), Google Workspace (email/docs)</li>
    <li><strong>Professional advisers:</strong> Lawyers, accountants and auditors under confidentiality obligations</li>
    <li><strong>Law enforcement:</strong> When required by Australian law or valid court order</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain personal data for as long as necessary to provide services and meet legal obligations. Transaction records are retained for 7 years as required by Australian tax law. You may request deletion of your account data at any time (subject to legal retention requirements).</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Under Australian Privacy Law, you have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
    <li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
    <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
    <li>Lodge a complaint with the <a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC)</a></li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@evotech.au">privacy@evotech.au</a>.</p>

  <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use essential cookies required for the website to function, and optional analytics cookies (Google Analytics) to understand how visitors use our site. You can disable non-essential cookies in your browser settings or via our cookie preferences.</p>

  <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including SSL/TLS encryption, access controls and regular security audits to protect your data. Payment processing is handled by PCI-DSS compliant providers — we never store credit card numbers.</p>

  <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
  <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and recommend you review their privacy policies.</p>

  <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of our website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

  <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
  <div class="policy-contact-box">
    <h3>Privacy Enquiries</h3>
    <p>📧 Privacy Officer: <a href="mailto:privacy@evotech.au">privacy@evotech.au</a></p>
    <p>📧 General: <a href="mailto:info@evotech.au">info@evotech.au</a></p>
    <p>📞 Phone: <a href="tel:+61466911816">+61 466 911 816</a></p>
    <p>📍 Perth, Western Australia, AU 6000</p>
  </div>

  {%- endif -%}

</div>

